			<item>
				<title>Improvements 2025</title>
				<link>https://xn--kleiderbgel-0hb.xn--blaufusstlpel-qmb.de/en/post/news-2025/</link>
				<pubDate>Sun, 19 Oct 2025 07:30:07 +0200</pubDate><author>mail@christianmahnke.de (Christian Mahnke)</author>
				<guid>https://xn--kleiderbgel-0hb.xn--blaufusstlpel-qmb.de/en/post/news-2025/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;This page has been slightly revised for an upcoming exhibition:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Navigation has been slightly improved&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The current coat hanger is now displayed on the home page&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The map is larger and has greater contrast&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;There is now a search function&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Loading time has been significantly reduced&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Statistics on the coat hangers are now available&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;An English translation is available&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;jQuery has been removed; the clothes rail visualization is now implemented with &lt;a href=&#34;https://swiperjs.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Swiper JS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;More information about the exhibition will be available in 2026!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
